name: DEATH - CUNT - JESUS #1
description:
I was at a party in the late 80's and everyone was on MDMA and there was this wild eyed kid giving everyone the thousand yard stare, saying nothing except "MY NAME IS DEATH CUNT JESUS" over and over again. There was a makeshift fire in the garden and he went and stood in it, repeating his mantra" I AM DEATH CUNT JESUS" before someone pulled him out with his trainers smoking. BAD TRIP I guess. Where is he now? Fuck knows, but i'll never forget him. 
Oh yeah, Trump's in it too, whatever that means.
